51
00:03:37,336 --> 00:03:40,214
All right, team, let's get ready
for the pre-race cheer. Ready?

52
00:03:40,339 --> 00:03:42,717
- Yes, sir!
- Ready?
- Yes, sir!

53
00:03:42,842 --> 00:03:46,387
All right,
one, two, three, toot!

54
00:03:46,512 --> 00:03:48,556
Who's the captain
of our crew?

55
00:03:48,681 --> 00:03:50,892
